## Design Summary
- Additive metadata only: writes signal_events rows + appends `[A6: ghost_closure absent_count=N]` note tag
- No DDL, no schema changes, no financial field writes
- Entry-price discriminator with 5% tolerance (matches A7 pattern)
- Idempotent: WHERE NOT EXISTS + changes() coupling for note dedup (TOCTOU-free)
- close_source IS NULL guard on note append (don't overwrite confirmed-close notes)
- close_source NEVER modified (provisional design — confirmed closures only mark status)
- try/except non-fatal wrapper: notification flow never blocked
- Single connection/transaction for event INSERT + note UPDATE

## Canary Protocol
- Trigger: next organic board_absent soft_close in prod → GHOST_CLOSURE event emitted
- GUARDIAN monitors first 10 occurrences for field-by-field validation
- Expected: PENDING until organic event materializes (may take hours/days)

